<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="数组去重" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#数组去重" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 数组去重</h2>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token doc-comment comment">/**
 * js数组去重(复杂数据有ID的情况下)
 * 方式一(hash)
 *
 * <span class="token keyword">@param</span> <span class="token class-name"><span class="token punctuation">{</span>Array<span class="token punctuation">}</span></span> <span class="token parameter">repeatArray</span> 含重复数据的数组
 * <span class="token keyword">@return</span> <span class="token class-name"><span class="token punctuation">{</span>Array<span class="token punctuation">}</span></span> 返回去重后的数据
 *
 */</span>
